Setting up DNS
==============

yum install bind bind-chroot bind-libs bind-utils

copy the contents of var_named from subversion to /var/named/chroot/var/named/
copy the contents of etc from subversion to /var/named/chroot/etc/

copy the key (secret) from /var/named/chroot/etc/rndc.key and put in /var/named/chroot/etc/named.conf, in the
  ddns_key section

service named start

chkconfig named on

